      "rationale": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. Mean absolute percentage error is 8.4%; all predictions fall within ±15% of measured values. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion satisfied for all candidate configurations. Exceeds Gradation 2 requirement; Gradation 3 achieved."
